### Criar usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Usuario Teste",
  "email": "usuario.teste@email.com",
  "senha": "123456"
}

### Listar usuarios
GET http://localhost:8080/usuarios

### Buscar usuario por id
GET http://localhost:8080/usuarios/1

### Criar categoria vinculada ao usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/categorias
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Alimentacao",
  "corHexadecimal": "#22C55E",
  "ativa": true,
  "usuarioId": 1
}

### Listar categorias
GET http://localhost:8080/categorias

### Criar conta vinculada ao usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/contas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "descricao": "Conta Nubank",
  "saldoAtual": 1500.75,
  "ativa": true,
  "usuarioId": 1
}

### Listar contas
GET http://localhost:8080/contas

### Criar transacao vinculada a conta e categoria
POST http://localhost:8080/transacoes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Mercado",
  "valor": 87.90,
  "dataHora": "2026-06-21T18:30:00",
  "origem": "MANUAL",
  "tipoMovimentacao": "DESPESA",
  "tipoPagamento": "PIX",
  "status": "CONCLUIDA",
  "contaId": 1,
  "categoriaId": 1
}

### Listar transacoes
GET http://localhost:8080/transacoes

### Atualizar transacao
PUT http://localhost:8080/transacoes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Mercado atualizado",
  "valor": 95.50,
  "dataHora": "2026-06-21T19:00:00",
  "origem": "MANUAL",
  "tipoMovimentacao": "DESPESA",
  "tipoPagamento": "CARTAO_DEBITO",
  "status": "CONCLUIDA",
  "contaId": 1,
  "categoriaId": 1
}

### Deletar transacao
DELETE http://localhost:8080/transacoes/1
